data.description: Back on the market!  Welcome home!  This home has been well maintained and is in the highly sought after community of Mont Belvieu and is zoned to Barbers Hills ISD.  This home is located on the North side of I10 and has easy access to all of Mont Belvieu with convenient access to the newly finished highway 99 (Grand Parkway) and I-10.  The home is a 5 bedroom and 3.5 bath.  The home has a large kitchen that opens up to a large living room.  The pool in the backyard was completed in 2018 and makes for the perfect backyard oasis.  There also are neighbors to the back, but there is a large drainage canal, so no one is extremely close in the back yard.
